    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the negotiation part, but i'm still nervous about how they actually handle the money while it's just sitting there. like, what is the actual responsibility of the person or company holding the funds? are they just sitting on it, or is there some kind of specific protocol for how they guard and manage those assets until the closing date?",
